README : For HW2
Author : Nipesh Roy <roy.nip@husky.neu.edu>

Description : Master-Worker multi process problem

How to Execute the code:
1.To create master and worker:
	Run : make

2.If object files are already present:
	Run : make clean

3. Example to run master
$ 	Run: ./master --worker_path ./worker --num_workers 5 --wait_mechanism
MECHANISM -x 2 -n 12

4. To test individual worker
	Run : ./worker -x 2 -n 3

NOTE:
The epoll mechanism is not fully functional and causes wrong result

